libs.content: find_program (xmllint_executable xmllint doc "the xmllint tool available in the xmllib package.")

find_program(sde_executable
        names "${sde_exec}"
        paths
            /usr/bin
            /usr/local/bin
            /opt/local/bin
        doc "intel software development emulator"
    )
find_library(bzip2_library_release names bz2 bzip2 ${_bzip2_paths} path_suffixes lib)

find_program(sphinx_executable
  names sphinx-build
  paths
    /usr/bin
    /usr/local/bin
    /opt/local/bin
  doc "sphinx documentation generator"
)

find_program( sphinx_executable
      names sphinx-build-${_version}
      paths
        /usr/bin
        /usr/local/bin
        /opt/loca/bin
      doc "sphinx documentation generator"
    )
